 * $Log: stripe.hpp,v $
 * Revision 1.7  1999/07/05 00:47:14  vitus
 * - addChild() gets additional flag "config sector valid", saved in child array
 *
 * Revision 1.6  1999/06/21 01:31:51  vitus
 * - corrected english spelling
